1
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:36,580
♪Flowers falling by the river again♪

2
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:38,840
♪Turning the clear waves red♪

3
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:44,600
♪Sparrows singing in celebration♪

4
00:00:46,290 --> 00:00:49,530
♪Calm years pass by the silent bustling city♪

5
00:00:49,530 --> 00:00:52,070
♪Sitting at home♪

6
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:58,260
♪No one knows love's outline like I do♪

7
00:00:58,550 --> 00:01:04,640
♪If one day the river breeze blows again♪

8
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:10,980
♪I won't be a mere reflection in the mirror♪

9
00:01:11,470 --> 00:01:17,540
♪Dreams can shatter; Memories remain♪

10
00:01:17,980 --> 00:01:21,230
♪Rich fragrance aids; Light ink writes♪

11
00:01:21,230 --> 00:01:28,090
♪In the deep red windows lies mundane dust♪

12
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:40,980
=Are You The One=

13
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,980
=Episode 13=

14
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:47,250
Especially with the news of the war.

15
00:01:48,390 --> 00:01:49,580
I feel

16
00:01:50,550 --> 00:01:51,780
even more

17
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,970
uneasy,

18
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,660
fearing that we might part forever

19
00:01:57,910 --> 00:01:59,020
and never meet again.

20
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:04,810
It must be laughable.

21
00:02:05,440 --> 00:02:06,280
But fortunately,

22
00:02:06,670 --> 00:02:08,190
you understand

23
00:02:08,190 --> 00:02:09,730
my twists and turns of emotions.

24
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:11,730
That's why we can sit here,

25
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,460
on this peaceful night.

26
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:16,530
Among these thousands of lights,

27
00:02:16,990 --> 00:02:18,410
we have our own.

28
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:20,010
My heart

29
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,290
feels settled now.

30
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:28,500
The world only knows

31
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:30,850
of the nobles and generals

32
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,530
who give their lives

33
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:33,730
and blood.

34
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,460
But in times of war,

35
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,690
this is what ordinary families are like.

36
00:02:39,990 --> 00:02:40,830
What?

37
00:02:41,010 --> 00:02:42,460
Aren't you an ordinary person?

38
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,200
Dear.

39
00:02:53,990 --> 00:02:55,040
Can you see

40
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:56,010
the three stars aligned?

41
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,180
One day,

42
00:03:00,590 --> 00:03:02,340
when Lord Huaiyang leads his army back,

43
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,780
he'll return from that direction.

44
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,620
But what if he doesn't win?

45
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,410
If he doesn't win,

46
00:03:15,990 --> 00:03:17,180
he'll still return from there,

47
00:03:18,550 --> 00:03:19,940
But he'll be

48
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,250
wrapped in horsehide,

49
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,010
returning in honor.

50
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:27,940
Come on.

51
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:30,410
Why do I need to know
where Lord Huaiyang will return from?

52
00:03:35,550 --> 00:03:36,410
You're right.

53
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:39,690
All I know is

54
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,640
we're a common family.

55
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:43,250
We may not reach great wealth,

56
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:46,110
but at least we can stay with our loved ones.

57
00:03:46,110 --> 00:03:46,970
That's enough.

58
00:04:00,390 --> 00:04:01,230
Dear.

59
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,340
Tonight is beautiful.

60
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,830
I've chosen the finest brocade

61
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:26,340
and the best materials.

62
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,820
This marriage certificate
can last for many years.

63
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:30,720
Your writing is nice.

64
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,970
You should write it.

65
00:04:35,590 --> 00:04:36,430
What's wrong?

66
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,700
I haven't decided what to write.

67
00:04:43,470 --> 00:04:45,000
I've already had someone draft it.

68
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:45,930
I'll read it to you.

69
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:55,640
The respected in-laws,
the Qiao family of Beizhou,

70
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:57,710
granted the engagement

71
00:04:57,710 --> 00:04:59,290
of Miss Miantang and Cui Jiu

72
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:00,930
of the capital.

73
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:03,050
Considering the ceremony and offering

74
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,850
to uphold the duties of the family

75
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:08,020
and the labors of the household,

76
00:05:08,270 --> 00:05:10,460
the long-standing virtues are held.

77
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,970
A lifelong union is pledged,

78
00:05:13,230 --> 00:05:14,700
written on this red paper,

79
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,490
bound by the pledge of autumn leaves.

80
00:05:27,150 --> 00:05:27,990
What's wrong?

81
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:30,410
Let me hold you for a moment.

82
00:05:31,350 --> 00:05:32,850
You can hold me for a lifetime.

83
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:42,670
♪The boat drifts♪

84
00:05:42,790 --> 00:05:43,780
If so,

85
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:45,660
I won't be able to write.

86
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:49,220
Read it to me, and I'll write it.

87
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:50,230
Okay.

88
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,850
♪Joke about the cause and effect♪

89
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:58,530
The respected in-laws,
the Qiao family of Beizhou,

90
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:01,300
granted the engagement of Miss Miantang

91
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:03,640
and Cui Jiu of the capital.

92
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:10,120
♪Choosing wrong;
With joys, sorrows, partings and reunions♪

93
00:06:10,740 --> 00:06:17,260
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

94
00:06:18,140 --> 00:06:23,540
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

95
00:06:23,540 --> 00:06:25,320
(Bound by the pledge)

96
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:32,130
♪A couple under the moonlight,
love shines like stars♪

97
00:06:32,380 --> 00:06:39,220
♪But hidden in the eyes for long,
fading and flickering♪

98
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:44,100
(Best wishes)

99
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:57,300
(Best wishes)

100
00:07:01,290 --> 00:07:07,840
♪Let go of the waves in the stream
in half a lifetime♪

101
00:07:08,350 --> 00:07:13,870
♪Let those dust and chaos go on endlessly♪

102
00:07:13,910 --> 00:07:14,930
Sorry.

103
00:07:15,790 --> 00:07:22,770
♪In this lifetime, my wish is to the vast sky;
There are many more♪

104
00:07:24,570 --> 00:07:31,280
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

105
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:38,900
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part;
Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

106
00:07:39,110 --> 00:07:46,020
♪A couple under the moonlight,
love shines like stars♪

107
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:53,270
♪But hidden in the eyes for long,
fading and flickering♪

108
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:14,310
♪If it weren't for travels far,
seeing clouds and snow♪

109
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:18,680
♪I can drink with you
and feel the separation♪

110
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:22,010
♪After enjoying spring flowers,
we sigh over the autumn moon♪

111
00:08:22,250 --> 00:08:28,980
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

112
00:08:29,380 --> 00:08:36,200
♪Time flows as we dream through four seasons♪

113
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:43,000
♪I wish to journey with you forever♪

114
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:49,180
♪Year after year♪

115
00:09:08,140 --> 00:09:11,180
(Letter of Divorce)

116
00:09:11,180 --> 00:09:12,700
I'm Cui Jiu of the capital.

117
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:16,140
My wife, Liu Miantang, and I

118
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:18,620
(Letter of Divorce)
are united in marriage,

119
00:09:18,740 --> 00:09:20,220
with deep affection

120
00:09:20,220 --> 00:09:21,660
and profound love.

121
00:09:22,780 --> 00:09:25,500
But now, with war raging,

122
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:26,940
the country is in turmoil.

123
00:09:26,940 --> 00:09:29,660
As an able-bodied man,

124
00:09:29,660 --> 00:09:31,500
I must grieve for the hardships of the people

125
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:33,740
and bear the suffering of the nation.

126
00:09:35,180 --> 00:09:37,980
Though born a merchant,
I will not shy away from duty,

127
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:41,900
nor evade responsibility due to low status.

128
00:09:43,260 --> 00:09:44,700
I have no grand ambitions,

129
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:48,020
but I should follow the example
of the countless men of Zhenzhou

130
00:09:48,020 --> 00:09:49,620
and serve my country with my life,

131
00:09:49,620 --> 00:09:51,460
even if it means death a hundred times.

132
00:09:54,180 --> 00:09:55,820
By the time you read this letter,

133
00:09:56,940 --> 00:09:59,540
I will have gone north with the Zhenzhou army.

134
00:09:59,820 --> 00:10:02,580
Life or death is uncertain.

135
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:06,380
I fear for your sorrow,

136
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:08,380
and that your youth will be wasted.

137
00:10:09,780 --> 00:10:12,700
So I am writing this letter of divorce.

138
00:10:13,340 --> 00:10:14,540
All properties

139
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:16,060
and money,

140
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,340
I leave to you.

141
00:10:18,140 --> 00:10:20,060
I hope Miantang will return

142
00:10:20,220 --> 00:10:21,580
to Beizhou with the servants,

143
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:23,220
and live a peaceful life.

144
00:10:24,780 --> 00:10:25,620
After this,

145
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:27,460
you are free to remarry.

146
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:29,780
There will be no disputes.

147
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:37,940
(Jinchen Tea)

148
00:10:37,940 --> 00:10:38,940
How is my face?

149
00:10:39,020 --> 00:10:39,900
Don't rush.

150
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:43,980
Alright. That's enough.

151
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:46,020
This time, the herbal smell is very strong.

152
00:10:46,660 --> 00:10:47,500
Binglan.

153
00:10:47,820 --> 00:10:48,660
Remember.

154
00:10:49,060 --> 00:10:50,500
Walk a bit slower later.

155
00:10:50,660 --> 00:10:52,460
You're supposed to be a bedridden patient.

156
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:54,660
- I know.
- Don't be nervous.

157
00:10:57,180 --> 00:10:58,300
- They're here.
- How is it?

158
00:10:58,580 --> 00:10:59,420
Pretty good.

159
00:10:59,430 --> 00:11:00,310
You go ahead.

160
00:11:02,060 --> 00:11:02,940
- Let's go.
- OK.

161
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:08,340
Before dawn,

162
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:10,220
the Lord had already set out.

163
00:11:10,460 --> 00:11:11,300
Go back, everyone.

164
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:13,420
Has the Lord left?

165
00:11:13,420 --> 00:11:14,740
Yes. Go back.

166
00:11:20,860 --> 00:11:21,780
What happened?

167
00:11:34,780 --> 00:11:35,620
Madam,

168
00:11:35,780 --> 00:11:36,900
the master

169
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:38,820
still cares about you.

170
00:11:38,940 --> 00:11:40,460
All the gold, silver,

171
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,620
and properties

172
00:11:41,620 --> 00:11:42,700
he could leave behind,

173
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:43,540
he left them

174
00:11:45,100 --> 00:11:46,300
for you.

175
00:11:52,020 --> 00:11:52,860
Nanny Li,

176
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:54,740
bring the contracts

177
00:11:54,740 --> 00:11:55,820
of Fangxie and Bicao.

178
00:11:56,100 --> 00:11:57,100
Free them.

179
00:11:58,460 --> 00:11:59,300
Moru,

180
00:11:59,580 --> 00:12:00,500
go and buy

181
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:01,900
some ropes and straps.

182
00:12:02,380 --> 00:12:04,100
Flat bands, woven tapes,

183
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:05,420
and thick ropes.

184
00:12:05,420 --> 00:12:06,300
These are essential.

185
00:12:06,980 --> 00:12:07,820
Madam,

186
00:12:08,180 --> 00:12:09,260
are you...?

187
00:12:09,420 --> 00:12:10,780
Didn't he want me to leave?

188
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:12,300
Since I'm not coming back,

189
00:12:12,460 --> 00:12:13,700
I'll take everything I can.

190
00:12:14,740 --> 00:12:16,220
Ms. Liu tricked you.

191
00:12:16,220 --> 00:12:17,540
Why go find her again?

192
00:12:18,460 --> 00:12:20,540
She claims to be my friend.

193
00:12:20,700 --> 00:12:22,060
I can't let this go like that.

194
00:12:22,580 --> 00:12:24,260
I must hear from her

195
00:12:24,260 --> 00:12:25,980
why she toyed with me.

196
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:34,140
(Cui Mansion)

197
00:12:50,660 --> 00:12:51,500
Miss He.

198
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:53,180
Where is your madam?

199
00:12:56,420 --> 00:12:57,260
Madam!

200
00:12:59,580 --> 00:13:00,420
Madam!

201
00:13:03,060 --> 00:13:03,900
Madam!

202
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:06,300
Nanny Li!

203
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:10,660
Madam!

204
00:13:12,380 --> 00:13:13,260
Madam!

205
00:13:14,580 --> 00:13:15,540
Nanny Li!

206
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:17,540
Where are they?

207
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:30,740
My Lord,

208
00:13:30,740 --> 00:13:32,660
the troops have been marching for days.

209
00:13:33,460 --> 00:13:35,460
The soldiers seem weary.

210
00:13:35,460 --> 00:13:37,140
Should we camp here?

211
00:13:37,140 --> 00:13:37,980
No.

212
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:40,260
The court has ordered us to reach

213
00:13:40,740 --> 00:13:42,020
Jinjia Pass within the month.

214
00:13:42,020 --> 00:13:43,100
This means

215
00:13:43,460 --> 00:13:44,940
we must cover fifty miles a day.

216
00:13:45,220 --> 00:13:46,380
If I'm lenient,

217
00:13:47,020 --> 00:13:48,220
I'd only be harming you all.

218
00:13:48,340 --> 00:13:49,180
My Lord.

219
00:13:49,380 --> 00:13:50,260
Pass the order

220
00:13:50,660 --> 00:13:51,580
to keep marching.

221
00:13:52,900 --> 00:13:54,820
Any delay will be punished by military law.

222
00:13:55,620 --> 00:13:56,460
Yes.

223
00:13:59,540 --> 00:14:00,380
My Lord.

224
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:02,020
My Lord, the madam...

225
00:14:02,020 --> 00:14:03,940
- What's wrong?
- The madam is fine.

226
00:14:07,100 --> 00:14:08,300
After receiving the letter,

227
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:10,260
she dismissed Fangxie and Bicao.

228
00:14:10,460 --> 00:14:12,100
Then she asked me to buy some supplies.

229
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:13,140
When I returned,

230
00:14:13,140 --> 00:14:14,580
she and Nanny Li were gone.

231
00:14:14,700 --> 00:14:16,340
Nanny Li left a message for the guards.

232
00:14:16,540 --> 00:14:17,980
She said the madam couldn't wait

233
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:20,140
and left with her and the money.

234
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:22,460
Rest assured.

235
00:14:22,620 --> 00:14:23,620
Per your orders,

236
00:14:23,900 --> 00:14:25,380
Fan Hu and the guys are following her.

237
00:14:28,300 --> 00:14:29,180
Nothing else?

238
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:32,980
Else?

239
00:14:33,220 --> 00:14:34,260
- You mean...?
- Crying?

240
00:14:34,820 --> 00:14:35,660
Ranting?

241
00:14:36,740 --> 00:14:38,220
Panic and cursing?

242
00:14:39,660 --> 00:14:41,100
Like that. What are you thinking?

243
00:14:41,940 --> 00:14:42,780
Nothing.

244
00:14:43,220 --> 00:14:44,100
After receiving it,

245
00:14:44,100 --> 00:14:45,340
the madam handled it calmly,

246
00:14:45,340 --> 00:14:46,380
without any fuss.

247
00:14:50,100 --> 00:14:52,620
She focused on taking the money,

248
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:54,380
just as I expected.

249
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:57,460
She didn't even pretend

250
00:14:57,460 --> 00:14:58,300
to cry?

251
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:00,220
No.

252
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:06,340
My Lord, I speculate

253
00:15:06,940 --> 00:15:07,980
she's following

254
00:15:07,980 --> 00:15:09,380
your letter's advice,

255
00:15:09,380 --> 00:15:10,980
returning to her family to live well.

256
00:15:11,140 --> 00:15:12,820
You should be glad

257
00:15:12,820 --> 00:15:13,940
the burden is gone.

258
00:15:13,940 --> 00:15:14,780
Yes.

259
00:15:15,380 --> 00:15:16,540
I am glad.

260
00:15:17,860 --> 00:15:19,700
She's just like other women,

261
00:15:19,860 --> 00:15:21,540
knowing how to adapt

262
00:15:21,540 --> 00:15:22,740
and live peacefully.

263
00:15:23,420 --> 00:15:24,300
Very good.

264
00:15:28,980 --> 00:15:29,980
Everyone, move on.

265
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:31,340
Yes.

266
00:15:47,460 --> 00:15:48,380
That shopkeeper

267
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:50,100
is capable and kind.

268
00:15:50,420 --> 00:15:51,660
He just advised me

269
00:15:51,660 --> 00:15:52,740
where to change horses

270
00:15:52,740 --> 00:15:53,780
and dine.

271
00:15:54,380 --> 00:15:55,780
After crossing the state border,

272
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:57,220
it'll be barren mountains.

273
00:15:57,980 --> 00:15:58,980
The northwest is cold.

274
00:15:58,980 --> 00:16:01,020
Nanny Li, take care.

275
00:16:02,260 --> 00:16:03,100
Madam.

276
00:16:03,740 --> 00:16:04,580
Well.

277
00:16:05,260 --> 00:16:07,060
Where are we going?

278
00:16:09,380 --> 00:16:10,340
To Xizhou.

279
00:16:10,860 --> 00:16:12,460
To follow Lord Huaiyang's army.

280
00:16:32,260 --> 00:16:36,700
(Liu has left Lingquan
with her servants for Xizhou.)

281
00:16:40,180 --> 00:16:41,740
She's gone to Xizhou?

282
00:16:43,620 --> 00:16:46,060
Cui Xingzhou must have some skills

283
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:49,860
to make her so loyal.

284
00:16:51,860 --> 00:16:54,220
Given what I know of Liu Mingtang,

285
00:16:55,020 --> 00:16:57,340
she wouldn't be so sincere.

286
00:16:59,300 --> 00:17:01,180
You mean she knows something

287
