00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:30,020
(Xizhou)

293
00:17:33,020 --> 00:17:38,260
(Xizhou)

294
00:17:52,140 --> 00:17:53,140
Nanny Li, are you okay?

295
00:17:53,140 --> 00:17:54,460
