298
00:17:56,780 --> 00:17:57,620
Sure.

299
00:18:00,700 --> 00:18:01,540
Madam!

300
00:18:01,860 --> 00:18:02,700
Bandits!

301
00:18:06,660 --> 00:18:07,580
Come on!

302
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:08,900
Help!

303
00:18:16,940 --> 00:18:18,780
