305
00:18:21,820 --> 00:18:23,580
Madam, you can't go!

306
00:19:13,100 --> 00:19:14,100
The two bandits

307
00:19:14,220 --> 00:19:15,380
are already tied up.

308
00:19:15,700 --> 00:19:16,540
Good.

309
00:19:18,060 --> 00:19:19,980
Thank you, heroes, for your assistance.

310
00:19:20,820 --> 00:19:22,380
May I know your names?

311
00:19:22,860 --> 00:19:23,700
No, no.

312
00:19:24,180 --> 00:19:25,340
Madam.

313
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:26,660
Your bravery saved the day.

314
00:19:26,660 --> 00:19:27,500
No need to thank us.

315
00:19:27,700 --> 00:19:28,540
Madam?

316
00:19:31,060 --> 00:19:31,940
Sir.

317
00:19:32,180 --> 00:19:33,660
Have we met before?

318
00:19:43,100 --> 00:19:43,980
I am

319
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:45,940
Fan Hu,

320
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:48,020
also from Zhenzhou.

321
00:19:48,580 --> 00:19:50,700
We once met before.

322
00:19:52,460 --> 00:19:53,980
Madam,

323
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:56,220
at Lingquan Town,

324
00:19:56,580 --> 00:19:57,660
by the river,

325
00:19:58,220 --> 00:20:01,180
you ran...

326
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:02,740
- A porcelain shop.
- A porcelain shop.

327
00:20:04,340 --> 00:20:05,580
We three brothers

328
00:20:05,580 --> 00:20:07,100
were following the army,

329
00:20:07,100 --> 00:20:08,780
intending to join and fight.

330
00:20:09,060 --> 00:20:10,180
But unexpectedly,

331
00:20:10,540 --> 00:20:11,780
we found you in distress.

332
00:20:12,020 --> 00:20:13,260
As fellow townsmen,

333
00:20:13,260 --> 00:20:14,540
it was our duty to help.

334
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:16,260
We didn't expect

335
00:20:17,180 --> 00:20:19,020
to end up in such a sorry state.

336
00:20:20,940 --> 00:20:22,620
These are my brothers,

337
00:20:23,540 --> 00:20:24,380
Hu Ting

338
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:26,340
and Ying Zai.

339
00:20:27,820 --> 00:20:28,820
I see.

340
00:20:30,100 --> 00:20:31,460
I'm truly sorry

341
00:20:31,820 --> 00:20:34,140
for causing your injuries.

342
00:20:34,580 --> 00:20:36,100
It's okay.

343
00:20:37,620 --> 00:20:38,460
Nanny Li.

344
00:20:38,540 --> 00:20:40,180
Get some rice wine and dried meat

345
00:20:40,180 --> 00:20:41,500
to thank and reward these heroes.

346
00:20:42,220 --> 00:20:43,060
Yes.

347
00:20:43,380 --> 00:20:44,220
Thank you, Madam.

348
00:20:45,140 --> 00:20:45,980
Madam.

349
00:20:46,360 --> 00:20:48,100
What should we do with the two bandits?

350
00:20:56,620 --> 00:20:57,580
Earlier,

351
00:20:57,580 --> 00:20:58,780
I heard wolves howling nearby.

352
00:20:59,500 --> 00:21:01,220
Cut them and feed them

353
00:21:01,820 --> 00:21:02,860
