354
00:21:05,820 --> 00:21:06,740
Yes.

355
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:08,940
Oh, Nanny Li.

356
00:21:09,260 --> 00:21:11,260
Heat some ointment.

357
00:21:11,260 --> 00:21:12,140
