376
00:22:15,220 --> 00:22:16,220
Who else was with her?

377
00:22:16,620 --> 00:22:18,180
A woman dressed as a man, a coachman,

378
00:22:18,340 --> 00:22:19,180
and three men

379
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:21,300
claiming they want to join the army.

380
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:22,300
One is seriously injured.

381
00:22:22,660 --> 00:22:24,780
Madness, absolute madness.

382
00:22:25,660 --> 00:22:27,060
Following the army like this.

383
00:22:27,060 --> 00:22:28,460
What are they thinking?

384
00:22:29,620 --> 00:22:30,460
Understood.

385
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:31,420
Yes.

386
00:22:31,900 --> 00:22:33,300
- Huang Gui.
- Yes.

387
00:22:36,340 --> 00:22:37,260
Find me a set

388
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:38,420
of regular soldier's armor.

389
00:22:40,580 --> 00:22:41,420
Keep it quiet.

390
00:22:41,580 --> 00:22:42,420
Yes.

391
00:22:43,540 --> 00:22:44,380
Come on.

392
00:22:46,940 --> 00:22:48,020
Help me up a bit.

393
00:22:48,980 --> 00:22:49,820
Madam.

394
00:22:50,500 --> 00:22:52,020
Have some food first.

395
00:23:02,260 --> 00:23:03,220
Are you better?

396
00:23:03,220 --> 00:23:04,060
Yes.

397
00:23:04,420 --> 00:23:05,260
I can manage.

398
00:23:06,300 --> 00:23:07,260
Eat something.

399
00:23:09,060 --> 00:23:09,900
Thank you, Madam.

400
00:24:38,860 --> 00:24:41,420
Do you think you're Lord Huaiyang?

401
00:24:42,340 --> 00:24:43,660
He wanted to be dramatic,

402
00:24:44,100 --> 00:24:46,020
writing a letter to cancel the engagement

403
00:24:46,860 --> 00:24:48,100
for some lofty ideal.

404
00:24:48,100 --> 00:24:49,420
It's for his reputation.

405
00:24:49,780 --> 00:24:51,620
