406
00:24:51,620 --> 00:24:52,940
and write a divorce letter?

407
00:24:53,860 --> 00:24:55,620
Leaving for the army without a word.

408
00:24:56,140 --> 00:24:57,540
Did you ever think?

409
00:24:58,260 --> 00:24:59,740
Even at the front,

410
00:24:59,740 --> 00:25:01,620
the Lord won't lack women.

411
00:25:02,660 --> 00:25:03,820
When he returns,

412
00:25:04,260 --> 00:25:05,300
he'll have a higher rank,

413
00:25:05,300 --> 00:25:06,300
wealth, and fine clothes.

414
00:25:07,460 --> 00:25:08,740
But you, in a moment of impulse,

415
00:25:08,740 --> 00:25:09,780
divorced your wife

416
00:25:10,500 --> 00:25:11,980
and gave away your assets.

417
00:25:12,140 --> 00:25:13,580
Do you think people will praise you

418
00:25:13,580 --> 00:25:14,540
for making sacrifices?

419
00:25:15,620 --> 00:25:17,020
Have the books driven you mad?

420
00:25:20,820 --> 00:25:22,620
If you truly wish to serve the country

421
00:25:22,980 --> 00:25:25,060
and fulfill your ambitions,

422
00:25:26,420 --> 00:25:27,980
discuss it with me properly.

423
00:25:27,980 --> 00:25:29,220
Will I stop you from that?

424
00:25:32,580 --> 00:25:33,780
If you die in battle,

425
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:37,660
I'll bring you home, no matter how far.

426
00:25:40,620 --> 00:25:42,740
But you wrote a letter to dismiss me.

427
00:25:45,340 --> 00:25:46,780
Do you see me

428
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:49,100
as just a selfish,

429
00:25:49,100 --> 00:25:50,540
cowardly woman?

430
00:25:59,020 --> 00:26:00,540
Who told you to write a divorce letter?

431
00:26:00,740 --> 00:26:02,140
Who told you to write that?

432
00:26:28,300 --> 00:26:29,780
I was wrong. I was wrong.

433
00:26:31,060 --> 00:26:32,140
I was wrong. I was wrong.

434
00:26:33,100 --> 00:26:34,260
It's all my fault.

435
00:26:42,060 --> 00:26:43,660
She must have been targeted

436
00:26:44,020 --> 00:26:45,740
as soon as she left Lingquan Town.

437
00:26:46,380 --> 00:26:48,700
