438
00:26:48,860 --> 00:26:50,460
that Madam was chasing after you.

439
00:26:50,780 --> 00:26:52,260
They set up an ambush

440
00:26:52,260 --> 00:26:53,340
on the necessary route.

441
00:26:55,180 --> 00:26:56,500
It's my incompetence

442
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:57,700
that put Madam in danger.

443
00:26:57,980 --> 00:26:58,820
Please, My Lord...

444
00:27:01,660 --> 00:27:02,860
Please punish me.

445
00:27:11,260 --> 00:27:13,100
When we were ambushed in the mountains,

446
00:27:13,100 --> 00:27:15,860
Madam saw Mr. Fan was seriously injured.

447
00:27:16,060 --> 00:27:17,740
She lent him her cloak

448
00:27:17,740 --> 00:27:20,100
to keep him warm.

449
00:27:20,540 --> 00:27:22,980
Despite the cold,

450
00:27:23,220 --> 00:27:25,500
she refused to wear that cloak.

451
00:27:28,740 --> 00:27:30,260
Why didn't you say so earlier?

452
00:27:30,460 --> 00:27:31,380
Why take it off?

453
00:27:33,580 --> 00:27:34,860
Just wear it.

454
00:27:36,700 --> 00:27:37,660
So, the assassin

455
00:27:37,660 --> 00:27:39,660
was subdued by her.

456
00:27:40,500 --> 00:27:41,380
And your life

457
00:27:42,020 --> 00:27:43,140
was saved by her too.

458
00:27:44,220 --> 00:27:45,140
Yes.

459
00:27:47,300 --> 00:27:48,140
Find a physician

460
00:27:48,660 --> 00:27:49,500
to treat his wounds.

461
00:27:50,180 --> 00:27:51,020
Yes.

462
00:28:11,620 --> 00:28:12,460
Go rest.

463
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:14,020
Get it treated.

464
00:28:18,060 --> 00:28:18,900
Thank you, My Lord.

465
00:28:47,580 --> 00:28:48,940
I am Lord Huaiyang.

466
00:28:49,260 --> 00:28:50,100
I was born

467
00:28:50,100 --> 00:28:51,780
to bring peace to the land.

468
00:28:52,060 --> 00:28:53,140
I'm responsible

469
00:28:53,300 --> 00:28:54,180
for my country.

470
00:28:54,540 --> 00:28:55,420
What right do I have

471
00:28:55,420 --> 00:28:56,580
to talk about love?

472
00:28:56,740 --> 00:28:58,460
I can't spend my life with only her.

473
00:28:58,900 --> 00:29:00,020
I won't promise her that.

474
00:29:01,060 --> 00:29:03,100
In the end, this is just a game.

475
00:29:03,780 --> 00:29:04,660
When the game's over,

476
00:29:05,020 --> 00:29:05,860
who would take

477
00:29:06,100 --> 00:29:07,420
the pieces away?

478
00:29:13,620 --> 00:29:15,540
