479
00:29:20,180 --> 00:29:22,940
I just wanted to check if you're okay.

480
00:29:25,300 --> 00:29:26,940
If you're fine, I'll leave.

481
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:31,740
Why aren't you leaving?

482
00:29:33,620 --> 00:29:35,020
I wanted to tell you.

483
00:29:38,700 --> 00:29:39,700
After the long journey,

484
00:29:41,500 --> 00:29:42,460
you must be tired.

485
00:29:47,020 --> 00:29:47,940
You forgot.

486
00:29:48,340 --> 00:29:49,740
My family runs an escort agency.

487
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:52,340
Traveling is common.

488
00:29:56,100 --> 00:29:57,340
I achieved merit days ago.

489
00:29:58,500 --> 00:29:59,940
The general appointed me

490
00:30:01,180 --> 00:30:02,580
