491
00:30:03,500 --> 00:30:04,860
He also promoted me to a centurion.

492
00:30:07,340 --> 00:30:08,300
That's good news.

493
00:30:09,100 --> 00:30:10,340
Since you've been promoted,

494
00:30:11,700 --> 00:30:13,460
you should return soon,

495
00:30:13,940 --> 00:30:15,020
so you don't get punished

496
00:30:15,020 --> 00:30:16,340
by the general because of me.

497
00:30:22,820 --> 00:30:24,540
It will be even colder as we head west.

498
00:30:25,580 --> 00:30:27,500
You must also keep warm.

499
00:30:39,900 --> 00:30:41,260
You look worn out.

500
00:30:41,580 --> 00:30:42,780
Marching is tough.

501
00:30:44,340 --> 00:30:45,780
You must rest.

502
00:30:46,020 --> 00:30:47,020
I'm fine.

503
00:30:48,460 --> 00:30:51,260
Tomorrow, let the coachman follow the army.

504
00:30:51,260 --> 00:30:52,460
After reaching Jinjia Pass,

505
00:30:52,460 --> 00:30:54,180
I'll find a nearby village

506
00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:56,180
for you to rest.

507
00:30:57,340 --> 00:30:58,220
Okay.

