514
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:13,060
Right.

515
00:32:14,580 --> 00:32:15,580
Why is he here again?

516
00:32:16,060 --> 00:32:16,980
Is Zhen sick again?

517
00:32:16,980 --> 00:32:18,300
She isn't ill.

518
00:32:18,300 --> 00:32:20,140
