521
00:32:37,180 --> 00:32:39,020
Take a few servants and...

522
00:32:41,820 --> 00:32:42,660
Please.

523
00:32:51,620 --> 00:32:52,660
Who are you?

524
00:32:53,820 --> 00:32:54,980
Are you a physician?

525
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:56,980
I am.

526
00:32:57,860 --> 00:32:58,860
