549
00:34:06,220 --> 00:34:07,060
Father.

550
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:08,380
Look at this.

551
00:34:08,700 --> 00:34:10,220
Isn't this a misfortune for the family?

552
00:34:10,220 --> 00:34:11,540
He Zhen has done

553
00:34:11,540 --> 00:34:12,900
something so shameful

554
00:34:12,900 --> 00:34:14,740
and disgraceful.

555
00:34:15,740 --> 00:34:17,940
Not long after you left,

556
00:34:18,180 --> 00:34:20,300
this oily-faced pervert

557
00:34:20,300 --> 00:34:21,980
