564
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:42,040
How unfortunate.

565
00:34:42,180 --> 00:34:43,020
Father.

566
00:34:43,220 --> 00:34:44,420
Are you crazy out of worries?

567
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:45,820
Such a jerk.

568
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:49,900
Don't mind him.

569
00:34:49,900 --> 00:34:51,060
Untie me first.

570
00:35:01,660 --> 00:35:02,540
Zhen.

571
00:35:02,780 --> 00:35:04,780
