from that of the Lord.

647
00:38:17,620 --> 00:38:18,500
Moreover,

648
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:19,740
didn't the Lord

649
00:38:19,860 --> 00:38:21,980
have an engagement with Princess Lin'an?

650
00:38:22,260 --> 00:38:23,140
What happened?

651
00:38:23,820 --> 00:38:24,660
Yes.

652
00:38:24,820 --> 00:38:25,740
He was supposed

653
00:38:25,740 --> 00:38:26,660
