661
00:38:40,260 --> 00:38:41,780
how can he still hold his position

662
00:38:41,780 --> 00:38:42,820
as the Lord today?

663
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:44,500
If you ask me,

664
00:38:45,260 --> 00:38:46,500
after all,

665
00:38:46,500 --> 00:38:47,700
he let me go today.

666
00:38:48,140 --> 00:38:49,140
It means

667
00:38:50,220 --> 00:38:51,860
