677
00:39:18,380 --> 00:39:19,220
Good.

678
00:39:19,580 --> 00:39:20,580
That's great.

679
00:39:20,660 --> 00:39:21,500
Good news.

680
00:39:21,540 --> 00:39:22,940
A happy event indeed.

681
00:39:24,980 --> 00:39:25,820
Miss He,

682
00:39:26,020 --> 00:39:27,100
