686
00:39:35,940 --> 00:39:37,220
Despicable quacks

687
00:39:37,220 --> 00:39:38,260
can't be trusted.

688
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:40,980
Ignoble people like you

689
00:39:41,500 --> 00:39:42,900
are indeed in cahoots

690
00:39:43,460 --> 00:39:44,660
with your friend.

691
00:39:46,660 --> 00:39:47,500
Miss,

692
00:39:47,980 --> 00:39:48,820
you know that, huh?

693
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:50,380
I thought Liu Miantang

694
00:39:50,380 --> 00:39:52,020
was pretending to be confused.

695
00:39:52,340 --> 00:39:54,260
Now, I know you are Lord Zhennan.

696
00:39:54,660 --> 00:39:55,980
I have

697
00:39:55,980 --> 00:39:57,860
figured things out thoroughly.

698
00:39:58,140 --> 00:39:59,100
Miantang

699
00:39:59,460 --> 00:40:00,580
was deceived by you all

700
00:40:00,780 --> 00:40:02,540
from the beginning to the end.

701
00:40:02,780 --> 00:40:04,180
It's not as you think.

702
00:40:06,900 --> 00:40:08,100
There are twists

703
00:40:08,260 --> 00:40:09,580
and turns in this matter,

704
00:40:09,740 --> 00:40:12,060
which concerns the peace of Zhenzhou.

705
00:40:14,180 --> 00:40:16,660
I cannot elaborate at this time.

706
00:40:17,260 --> 00:40:19,140
Is hiding his identity to keep a mistress

707
00:40:19,140 --> 00:40:20,740
related to the safety of the county?

708
00:40:21,820 --> 00:40:22,660
My Lord,

709
00:40:22,900 --> 00:40:24,140
don't tell me such pretty lies

710
00:40:24,140 --> 00:40:25,820
