of the powerful.

713
00:40:31,100 --> 00:40:32,580
I'm not lying to you about this.

714
00:40:33,300 --> 00:40:35,140
Lord Huaiyang has gone to the northwest

715
00:40:35,140 --> 00:40:36,220
and divorced Liu Miantang.

716
00:40:36,220 --> 00:40:37,860
They're no longer a couple anymore.

717
00:40:38,900 --> 00:40:40,460
Lord Huaiyang and I

718
00:40:40,620 --> 00:40:42,500
are not the kind of people

719
00:40:42,500 --> 00:40:44,100
who are blinded by lust as you think.

720
00:40:45,060 --> 00:40:46,100
I am here today

721
00:40:46,220 --> 00:40:47,500
to ask Mr. He for a convoy

722
00:40:47,500 --> 00:40:49,020
to deliver provisions.

723
00:40:50,020 --> 00:40:52,420
When the time comes,

724
00:40:52,540 --> 00:40:54,780
I will tell you everything.

725
00:40:56,460 --> 00:40:57,300
My Lord,

726
00:40:57,700 --> 00:40:59,540
I don't want to hear

727
00:41:00,300 --> 00:41:01,380
