728
00:41:06,300 --> 00:41:07,140
You...

729
00:41:08,220 --> 00:41:09,140
You infuriate me.

730
00:41:12,420 --> 00:41:13,260
Mr. He.

731
00:41:13,620 --> 00:41:14,460
Sorry for the wait.

732
00:41:14,500 --> 00:41:15,340
My Lord.

733
00:41:15,460 --> 00:41:16,580
- Please.
- Please.

734
00:41:19,100 --> 00:41:19,940
Please.

735
00:41:25,460 --> 00:41:26,460
To be honest,

736
00:41:27,220 --> 00:41:28,060
I am currently

737
00:41:28,220 --> 00:41:29,940
