745
00:41:45,060 --> 00:41:45,900
So,

746
00:41:46,300 --> 00:41:47,140
do you agree?

747
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:49,860
That's great.

748
00:41:50,420 --> 00:41:52,460
Then no one else will have any objections.

749
00:41:52,780 --> 00:41:54,700
I am the head of the family,

750
00:41:55,020 --> 00:41:57,340
