766
00:42:27,060 --> 00:42:28,340
It's our duty.

767
00:42:29,580 --> 00:42:30,580
Not at all.

768
00:42:31,100 --> 00:42:32,340
- Please.
- Please.

769
00:42:36,780 --> 00:42:37,620
